    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台“0元开店”试运营管理规则》公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1318884824836186112",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展，针对《<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=915123374395625472\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台\"0元开店\"试运营管理规则</a></span></span></span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">》</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行调整<span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年12月25日- 2025年12月31日，规则预计于2026年1月1日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">核心调整点：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">针对部分表述进行优化，将参与&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营的类目单独以表格形式呈现，同时在《<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\"><a style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=638209647311982592\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</a></span></span>》删除【试运营阶段】字段。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">修订后内容如下：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 id=\"heading-1\" style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 24pt; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二章 试运营规则</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 24pt; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">从2023年4月1日起，针对新入驻京东开放平台的POP模式商家，部分类目支持&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营，即试运营期间不缴纳保证金，试运营结束进入正式运营阶段后再缴纳保证金，</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #c55a11;\">参与&ldquo;0元开店&rdquo;试运营的类目可详见：0元试运营类目明细。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: var(--Jd-color-fill-300) #fafafa; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #c55a11;\">注：具体明细以最终公示为准。</span></p>",
